(197, 1, '2013-06-18 04:50:53', '2013-06-18 04:50:53', '<p>Melissas love for life is fueled by working out, traveling and food.<p>\r\n<p>\r\nWhether she is working on her latest workout, her healthy diet recipes or planning the next trip, Melissas energy and enthusiasm toward helping you attain your health goals is clear. Driven by her holistically-balanced approach, Melissas message about full health resonates with all who hear her speak.\r\n </p>\r\n<p>\r\nMelissas passion personifies Failure Is Not An Option. Her background as a professional fitness model and body building competitor lead to a dynamic energy-filled event wherever she presents. Attending a Melissa workshop will have you embracing your own FINAO as you unleash the athlete within.</p>', 'Melissa Tucker', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'melissa-tucker', '', '', '2013-10-22 08:43:02', '2013-10-22 08:43:02', '', 0, 'http://biziindia.com/finaospeakers/?post_type=speakers&#038;p=197', 0, 'speakers', '', 0),
