(363, 1, '2013-06-25 07:31:48', '2013-06-25 07:31:48', '<div class="content-run-text">\r\n<p class="padding-10pixels"><span class="orange">I am an experienced speaker, how do I submit my materials for consideration to your agency?</span></p>\r\n<p class="padding-10pixels" style="margin-left:10px;">Thank you for your interest in joining the FINAO Speakers Bureau.  We are always interested in hearing from individuals who would like to be added to our team of great speaker. If you exude FINAO and would like to be considered for our team please submit the following information:\r\n1. Biography\r\n2. Video - this should be a full length video of you speaking to a youth or business audience. Please do not send demo videos, they will not be looked at or returned.\r\n3. Reference Letters - please include at least 3 references from individuals who have seen your presentation. (Preferably these should be clients who have hosted you in the last year.)\r\n4. Photo - this does not have to be an 8X10, but it must be a professional photo\r\n5. Fee schedule - please describe your fee structure and travel requirements (i.e. are weekend dates different rates than weekdays? Does the event location affect the price? Etc)</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="padding-10pixels" style="margin-left:10px;">Please mail materials to-\r\nThe FINAO Speakers Bureau\r\nATTN: Potential speaker\r\nPO Box 1488\r\nLafayette, CA 94549</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="padding-10pixels"><span class="orange font-14px padding-14 pixels">Ive never booked a speaker before, where do I start?</span></p>\r\n<p class="padding-10pixels" style="margin-left:10px;">If you have a good idea of what you are looking for, take a moment to check out our list of top-notch speakers. Then, either submit a request form on-line or give us a call directly to discuss your event. Please never hesitate to contact us by phone. We would be happy to suggest speakers, answer any questions you have, and send you additional materials such as demo videos and written materials.</p>\r\n</div></div>', 'Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'faq', '', '', '2013-06-25 12:22:15', '2013-06-25 12:22:15', '', 0, 'http://finaospeakers.com/?page_id=363', 0, 'page', '', 0),
